    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "but that just feels like putting a bandaid on a gunshot wound. all those small changes won't matter if the fundamental systems are broken. it's like watching a slow motion train wreck and being told to enjoy the scenery or plant a tree. it's hard to find the motivation to keep existing in a world that's essentially a sinking ship. how can anyone find real meaning in a future that isn't even guaranteed to exist?",
